metacity: metacity (GNOME Window Manager)
metacity:
metacity: Metacity (rhymes with "capacity") is a compositing window manager used 
metacity: by default in the GNOME desktop environment. The development of Metacity 
metacity: was started by Havoc Pennington and it is released under the GNU General 
metacity: Public License.
metacity: 
metacity: Although Metacity is part of the GNOME project and designed to integrate 
metacity: into the GNOME desktop, it does not require GNOME to run, and GNOME can be 
metacity: used with different window managers. Metacity is implemented in GTK+, which 
metacity: makes it themeable and makes it blend in with other GTK+ applications.
